data.description: This cozy home in one of the most desirable neighborhoods in Elk City will not disappoint! It boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with a beautiful wood burning fireplace and a dining area. There are gorgeous mature trees that encompass the home and provide plenty of shade in the backyard. This the perfect home that you don't want to miss out on!
